         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Phileas to Zenon greeting. Be good enough to [- - -] (several lines too fragmentary to be translated). Farewell. And if there is better stone by you, take it in exchange.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.</ab>
